  .article-section.article-section-right-image.text-first.article-half-page-image-floated
    .article-text
      %h3
        Summer outfits and holidays – final thought

      .article-image.aspect-1
        -image_url = image_path("blog/white-trainers/white-trainers.jpg")
        =image_tag(image_url, alt: "A pair of clean, new, unworn, white tennis shoes.")
        %figcaption
          Photo by
          =link_to('rawpixel.com', 'https://www.freepik.com/free-photo/white-canvas-sneakers-unisex-footwear-fashion_15850233.htm')
          on Freepik

      %p
        After my week away I realised one thing: I was not ready to give up my white trainers.
        Why would I?
        They are amazing.
        They make my life so much easier.
        They always make my outfits look even better than I imagined.
        They are perfect for summer!

      %p
        Do you see where this is going?
        If you own a pair, do you feel ready to give them up yet?
        My advice is to wear your white trainers all summer if you want to.
        Wherever you go and whatever you do, take them with you.

      %p
        If you still love them?
        Then wear them.
        Wear them all day and all night if you want to, because honestly these lovely little babies just became a true classic and they will be around for longer than you might think.


